{"tid":844510,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"係窮呀，屌你個西班牙+巴黎遊記","createTime":"2018-10-02T02:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T08:19:07.000Z","uid":16584,"like":16,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"68f4a0ac156612a7e601be9bdfb31831b0ab6d4b","tid":844510,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"有錢冇時間，有時間通常就冇錢，比著誠哥話用佢副身家同我交換我廿幾歲既青春，我真係諗三秒都覺得不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正所謂有仔襯嫩生，所以去旅行都係早去早享受<br />\n<br />\n自從上次寫完新北市嗰個post之後，我就的起心肝拎返起二月嗰時去西班牙同巴黎啲相出嚟睇，嗰時啱啱好係返上一份工之前最自由自在既時候，雖然做每樣野都要睇實銀包做人，但睇返相都覺得開心，好想喺度同大家分享尻噏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/000850_3373e6df6917a1c2cb5fddc74ced1c84.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F000850_3373e6df6917a1c2cb5fddc74ced1c84.JPG&h=bbd5ab35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/000908_69ed63429ed184b4dfb0e1b0cc19f874.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F000908_69ed63429ed184b4dfb0e1b0cc19f874.JPG&h=d5be9ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/001715_bc5cb2aa38987a23a34c66f7b5888627.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F001715_bc5cb2aa38987a23a34c66f7b5888627.JPG&h=b2518324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/001736_cc1c4a082f33c493ca044e5b1f9c5d04.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F001736_cc1c4a082f33c493ca044e5b1f9c5d04.JPG&h=2725f615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一個post-不要工作，去新北市！裸辭離開香港一個月！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/804440/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/804440/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">之前開咗個fb page，諗住間唔中可以update下〜有興趣可以入去睇下呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kapei898hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkapei898hk%2F&d=bkMff%2BmN1HGnJVfal0EyERv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3054d950\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kapei898hk/</a></span>"},{"pid":"57d5368f3fb14798ef387a2f0227dc6be9a5e4e8","tid":844510,"uid":195344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"見到標題就皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ee502ee8121c5f8cd1ece91c874369170d41e4","tid":844510,"uid":16584,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"1.一日用咗八個鐘車來回粉紅色湖 拼車偽road trip初體驗<br />\n<br />\n嗰時係同朋友一齊去，不過出發前大家都忙冇點plan，所以喺西班牙嗰時先驚覺原來馬德里同想去嗰個粉紅色湖Laguna Salada de Torrevieja之間係咁撚遠，而且原本打算搭火車去到附近一個地中海海邊城市Torrevieja再搭車去，點知連火車飛都貴到成千蚊來回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果我突然間醒起有個fd之前同我講佢用一個外國拼車app blablacar上網同人拼車，由荷蘭搭車摌落巴黎<br />\n於是我就拿拿臨上網check check咁樣去要幾錢，冇記錯三百幾蚊來回就得，但要搭成八個鐘車來回cls（後尾拼車嗰時同人吹水佢地都覺得我地cls一日來回玩咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同揸車嗰個約好咗第二日朝早七點半喺一個火車站外面等，一去到已經見到司機同另外嗰位乘客吹住水咁等緊我地。<br />\n司機係一個目測米九既伯伯，啲鬍鬚同頭髮都灰灰白白。 而另外嗰個乘客就係一個三十頭既男人，唔太高170左右，好典型西班牙男人既體型。佢地一嚟就同我地握晒手互相介紹一下，然後就開車了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105513_f11af1aca660e519fe90c31fda81ef24.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105513_f11af1aca660e519fe90c31fda81ef24.JPG&h=e4c43cbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105527_5a1585b0acd0326603f36eb1a04ee20d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105527_5a1585b0acd0326603f36eb1a04ee20d.JPG&h=76820714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地坐前排瘋狂尻噏，我同朋友坐後排半睡半醒咁系迷緊，夢遊住咁影下風景相又同佢地吹下水，時間都唔係話真係過得好慢，好快就十點零鐘。司機話要去前面個小鎮停低飲杯咖啡抖抖先，太好了我都想落車伸展下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105621_3f6298cb35da59f5f1beca0fb698aeda.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105621_3f6298cb35da59f5f1beca0fb698aeda.JPG&h=4ec9b213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105641_82d74b84221ea5704ddd130f5f505534.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105641_82d74b84221ea5704ddd130f5f505534.JPG&h=793d383e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105550_2b38859fe6fcdfc9a20dcea34c12feb6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105550_2b38859fe6fcdfc9a20dcea34c12feb6.JPG&h=57430a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n司機好熟路咁帶咗我地入間餐館仔，好熟路咁叫咗杯咖啡再請埋我地飲野，之後hea咗廿分鐘左右去埋廁所就繼續上路，覺得個小鎮好似人都唔多個咁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105704_c31c264928d2d8bb09851a5305a9daaf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105704_c31c264928d2d8bb09851a5305a9daaf.JPG&h=c3366ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105715_49e6f154340b678ddfba1d08524214b6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105715_49e6f154340b678ddfba1d08524214b6.JPG&h=d3d3dc4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105730_2f5fbd8703baf541950b6bb1948001a8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105730_2f5fbd8703baf541950b6bb1948001a8.JPG&h=aad73df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105909_1448c9b11754e5506bcb28403e1514f4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105909_1448c9b11754e5506bcb28403e1514f4.JPG&h=9d47a056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105901_e7708fe1eeb40bc8d1845eb0445b74ec.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105901_e7708fe1eeb40bc8d1845eb0445b74ec.JPG&h=213492aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如是者又搭咗兩個零鐘，呀司機突然之間問：「其實你地嗰個湖喺邊？」<br />\n???????????!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!我心諗唔撚係呀搭咗咁多個鐘你依家先嚟問我<br />\n好彩依個世界係有google map，搞搞下佢地話車我地去湖邊停一陣一齊落車影下相，之後就再去Torrevieja放低我地，因為個湖附近乜柒都冇<br />\n<br />\n兜兜轉轉終於搵到個位泊車，落車已經見到個湖，但實物冇想象中咁粉紅，上網睇話原來要睇時間睇溫度嚟先得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105755_0e65c09737c7efcf8bf16e854b103ed7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105755_0e65c09737c7efcf8bf16e854b103ed7.JPG&h=a5032c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（覺得依張佢地有啲gay味滲出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105806_7eecba3cffc3e672ff1b670b19fdcb7c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105806_7eecba3cffc3e672ff1b670b19fdcb7c.JPG&h=dc3f2847&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/105838_a807688be61c93ee70226ad17956934f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F105838_a807688be61c93ee70226ad17956934f.JPG&h=a9a2de41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以好似中咗少少伏，不過唔緊要！因為下篇講嗰個Torrevieja小城個海好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ed368dbd16a636e0f42cb04da44aee68559b21","tid":844510,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57d5368f3fb14798ef387a2f0227dc6be9a5e4e8","tid":844510,"uid":195344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"見到標題就皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43afd5ad2ef9afc16cb3780f5a4164cf8b349360","tid":844510,"uid":16154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:34:39.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"92fb9af56e5f49b113e2c6bcb8d034939faaa3fc","tid":844510,"uid":34008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c5e727bdfe6d55736e93fa98fa32ba2e1dace4f6","tid":844510,"uid":67779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f4a0ac156612a7e601be9bdfb31831b0ab6d4b","tid":844510,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"有錢冇時間，有時間通常就冇錢，比著誠哥話用佢副身家同我交換我廿幾歲既青春，我真係諗三秒都覺得不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正所謂有仔襯嫩生，所以去旅行都係早去早享受<br />\n<br />\n自從上次寫完新北市嗰個post之後，我就的起心肝拎返起二月嗰時去西班牙同巴黎啲相出嚟睇，嗰時啱啱好係返上一份工之前最自由自在既時候，雖然做每樣野都要睇實銀包做人，但睇返相都覺得開心，好想喺度同大家分享尻噏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/000850_3373e6df6917a1c2cb5fddc74ced1c84.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F000850_3373e6df6917a1c2cb5fddc74ced1c84.JPG&h=bbd5ab35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/000908_69ed63429ed184b4dfb0e1b0cc19f874.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F000908_69ed63429ed184b4dfb0e1b0cc19f874.JPG&h=d5be9ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/001715_bc5cb2aa38987a23a34c66f7b5888627.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F001715_bc5cb2aa38987a23a34c66f7b5888627.JPG&h=b2518324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/001736_cc1c4a082f33c493ca044e5b1f9c5d04.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F001736_cc1c4a082f33c493ca044e5b1f9c5d04.JPG&h=2725f615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一個post-不要工作，去新北市！裸辭離開香港一個月！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/804440/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/804440/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">之前開咗個fb page，諗住間唔中可以update下〜有興趣可以入去睇下呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kapei898hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkapei898hk%2F&d=bkMff%2BmN1HGnJVfal0EyERv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3054d950\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kapei898hk/</a></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"又係你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次又睇邊隊，又買咩標本呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195226534791164853f3527c90649a02f1f2cbb0","tid":844510,"uid":16584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:26:06.000Z","msg":"2.錯有錯著 嚟咗一個面朝地中海既西班牙渡假小城 <br />\n<br />\n上回講到去完粉紅色湖，咁我地就上返車繼續向終點Torrevieja小城駛去〜<br />\n喺前一晚未搵個湖點去之前，我根本聽都未聽過依個地方，而且我地本身係打算留喺湖邊9fing到完場，好彩多得司機同呀西班牙佬提議，唔係我諗我都冇乜機會會特登過嚟依度咁偏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半個鐘後，車外既風景慢慢由滾滾紅塵變成一幢幢三四層樓既民居，烈日當空下好多商店都冇開，而開得既都係餐廳同埋賣紀念品同泳衣既舖頭（姐係長洲嗰種，exact7ly係）。<br />\n<br />\n由於我地完全對依個地方冇概念，所以佢地喺邊度放低我地都冇所謂，不過我都係落車前先知，原來司機同呀西班牙佬喺依程車入面已經be咗fd，西班牙佬仲話落車後會去司機屋企作客喎，真開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而我地睇一睇地圖見行出兩條間就係海，好興奮咁尻衝出去睇下，順便搵下有咩食〜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120711_2347ebd86dbbe98856025e50951f7c3f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120711_2347ebd86dbbe98856025e50951f7c3f.JPG&h=7c025555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一轉彎行出去見到個海，靚到好似拍戲咁，海邊既城市，海邊既餐廳，海邊既西文路牌，全部野喺陽光底下都閃閃發光。行咗幾分鐘就見到一間餐廳，白色外牆座立喺海上面，對住一面無際既地中海，任由海風穿透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120546_b95af139bd97220a495a69b151419b70.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120546_b95af139bd97220a495a69b151419b70.JPG&h=a815eae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120733_f62fa18f79df76cb7e61ec3c847d11ca.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120733_f62fa18f79df76cb7e61ec3c847d11ca.JPG&h=415c4afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇睇到價錢就入咗去，不過感覺上西班牙物價都唔高，食咗個pizza同西班牙炒飯加啤酒小食，埋單冇記錯都係百零二百一位都合理既。<br />\n<br />\n食完飯就喺附近行下坐下沙灘，亞洲面孔喺依度真係完全係零，大部分人嚟依度都似嚟渡假多過本地人，因為當我地行返出大街，發現極多屋都係空置同埋好多地產舖，除咗沙灘之外條街真係人影都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120626_9aadc655a71c7e93c0a846a23f317dbe.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120626_9aadc655a71c7e93c0a846a23f317dbe.JPG&h=63a89428&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120755_42acce9bb4cff4e1e40acce4926acb38.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120755_42acce9bb4cff4e1e40acce4926acb38.JPG&h=7803a83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120804_e0faf52cd0ed2f313a433403b09553d4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120804_e0faf52cd0ed2f313a433403b09553d4.JPG&h=a65909ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120817_8052f06b79d137f3fe6e7231048e0219.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120817_8052f06b79d137f3fe6e7231048e0219.JPG&h=2fbb098a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姐係九十幾萬就買到樓了依度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/121017_48ac8adbd9dd7949342e5c5677551dbf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F121017_48ac8adbd9dd7949342e5c5677551dbf.JPG&h=2af58bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/121043_960744d7bdb2bece9bef7eb9d0887be0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F121043_960744d7bdb2bece9bef7eb9d0887be0.JPG&h=441117f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/121047_35dccbbbd4a01ebb2d37c4304aaa23e8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F121047_35dccbbbd4a01ebb2d37c4304aaa23e8.JPG&h=4d3c8e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/121054_ff206133f5f233f84de4047f3f8c1be6.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F121054_ff206133f5f233f84de4047f3f8c1be6.JPG&h=1558adcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/121103_6406af3668d99f8bac2b505d026643de.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F121103_6406af3668d99f8bac2b505d026643de.JPG&h=bd1a74fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/121118_0d365f30d42718d4a90de0fe1d787e0d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F121118_0d365f30d42718d4a90de0fe1d787e0d.JPG&h=364e090b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120652_06a69d0fdb8a3742c6a4ef005f4c1032.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120652_06a69d0fdb8a3742c6a4ef005f4c1032.JPG&h=f713feb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快就已經五點，夠鐘要去搭車返馬德里，今次回程既係既司機既係一對情侶嚟，嚟依度玩咗成個星期，佢地話車埋我地返去可以省返啲油錢喎〜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120920_413bd9c165706d7164858c9b3c447bdb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120920_413bd9c165706d7164858c9b3c447bdb.JPG&h=a10796fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又係揸到咁上下就去咗油站停一停抖下，油街外面就係公路，真係行出去都會比車車死，周圍又好空曠，係犯罪既好地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120931_6c131b48222fcf81c77f4bd4e219161d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120931_6c131b48222fcf81c77f4bd4e219161d.JPG&h=d3de4d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/120856_c6c9c4f5829a75b0bd0984407a4029c5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F120856_c6c9c4f5829a75b0bd0984407a4029c5.JPG&h=7fb5cc38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過返去依轉好快，好似開到200都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔識揸車的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完~"},{"pid":"682d23bb8f3b89415503f5091940c47a49a5f6b9","tid":844510,"uid":12251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"巴打個個月都去旅行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21551d335c3b0fda533137058267eb4c8aba275e","tid":844510,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5e727bdfe6d55736e93fa98fa32ba2e1dace4f6","tid":844510,"uid":67779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f4a0ac156612a7e601be9bdfb31831b0ab6d4b","tid":844510,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"有錢冇時間，有時間通常就冇錢，比著誠哥話用佢副身家同我交換我廿幾歲既青春，我真係諗三秒都覺得不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正所謂有仔襯嫩生，所以去旅行都係早去早享受<br />\n<br />\n自從上次寫完新北市嗰個post之後，我就的起心肝拎返起二月嗰時去西班牙同巴黎啲相出嚟睇，嗰時啱啱好係返上一份工之前最自由自在既時候，雖然做每樣野都要睇實銀包做人，但睇返相都覺得開心，好想喺度同大家分享尻噏下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/000850_3373e6df6917a1c2cb5fddc74ced1c84.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F000850_3373e6df6917a1c2cb5fddc74ced1c84.JPG&h=bbd5ab35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/000908_69ed63429ed184b4dfb0e1b0cc19f874.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F000908_69ed63429ed184b4dfb0e1b0cc19f874.JPG&h=d5be9ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/001715_bc5cb2aa38987a23a34c66f7b5888627.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F001715_bc5cb2aa38987a23a34c66f7b5888627.JPG&h=b2518324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/001736_cc1c4a082f33c493ca044e5b1f9c5d04.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F